# Technical stack

- Next.js 15 for the frontend
- Using Tailwind css for stying
- The routes are built inside src/app and if the url should be authenticated use src/app/(home) directory and put it inside
- External Rest API for the backend  
- All apis should have authentication unless the requirement say so
- Separate api url config for dev, test, and prod 
